cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.AI 

The paper focuses on pairwise learning to rank, which is a common problem in information retrieval (IR) and machine learning (ML). Therefore, cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) are the most likely categories. The paper also uses neural networks, which are a popular tool in many subfields of computer science, including natural language processing (cs.CL), computer vision (cs.CV), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
